&lt;p&gt;To add slider in any page, you need a bit of HTML and CSS, following is steps:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Edit any page.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Change to HTML Source by click [Source] button on Editor toolbar.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add you own slider like this:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
